{"tid":136138,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本推行「Happy Friday」鼓勵星期五3點收工","createTime":"2017-02-27T00:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T00:55:59.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6bd37fe6241b1f9150bcd559f1f94ecd2b8e23","tid":136138,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T00:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1670000/1671180/happyfriday_thumb_20170224T_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1670000%2F1671180%2Fhappyfriday_thumb_20170224T_1024.jpg&h=3fb65356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本企業加班文化盛行，導致不少社會問題，政府及商界開始由政策層面着手，減輕員工壓力。日本政府今日起實施「頂級星期五」（Premium Friday），鼓勵企業在每月的最後一個周五，允許員工在下午3時下班。<br />\n<br />\n當局冀能藉此刺激國內消費，民眾的工作與生活也能取得平衡。<br />\n<br />\n【延伸閱讀】 Sanrio新角色「衝吧烈子」　日本打工仔的吶喊<br />\n<br />\n不少大企陸續推出相關的獎勵措施，例如軟庫就會於今天提早下班，同時會向全公司1.8萬名正式員工發放每月1萬日圓（約690港元）的額外獎金，由於銷售門市繼續營業，門市員工則可自選提早下班的日子。<br />\n<br />\n糖果廠商森永則允許旗下1,349名員工今日可放半天或1天帶薪假，並且要求員工盡量減少跟工作活動及會議。<br />\n<br />\n百貨業、飲食業、旅遊業等紛推優惠乘機吸客，例如旅行社推出星期五傍晚出發的兩天半旅遊方案，希望增周末短途旅行的銷路，亦有飲品商連同食肆送出免費啤酒。<br />\n<img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1670000/1671180/FRIDAYAMAZON_j_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1670000%2F1671180%2FFRIDAYAMAZON_j_1024.jpg&h=f2e3c614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據官方網站，現時有3930間企業參與計劃。不過，據日本經濟新聞的調查，僅37%大型企業有意調整下班時間，約45%暫未有相關計劃。另一個調查更發現，僅3.4%的日本上班族表示，受惠於超值星期五；同時問及打算怎樣運用提早下班的休暇時間，58.5%人表示希望「在家悠閒度過」，似乎新政策對商業的作用暫時未必太大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/1671180/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%8E%A8%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%8CHappy%20Friday%E3%80%8D%20%20%20%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E4%BA%943%E9%BB%9E%E6%94%B6%E5%B7%A5?mtc=10018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1671180%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%258E%25A8%25E8%25A1%258C%25E3%2580%258CHappy%2520Friday%25E3%2580%258D%2520%2520%2520%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%258B%25B5%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%259C%259F%25E4%25BA%25943%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%25B7%25A5%3Fmtc%3D10018&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0LDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=e9be327f\" target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/1671180/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%8E%A8%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%8CHappy%20Friday%E3%80%8D%20%20%20%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E4%BA%943%E9%BB%9E%E6%94%B6%E5%B7%A5?mtc=10018</a>"},{"pid":"bed46a51882c67f5c4bd4a8714d96c4796f5bb2d","tid":136138,"uid":19450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T00:03:44.000Z","msg":"香港：繼續 OT"},{"pid":"76283e6d70bb561ad829082853e6a6c72dd89d27","tid":136138,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T00:11:13.000Z","msg":"一至四每人O多兩個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edc0a1ff39924e81e47c9429f22e6c58ad2bd30","tid":136138,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T00:11:39.000Z","msg":"日本人收工咪又係去陪老闆飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65212b1a37def994d1a12f94c4f38b8b25704e4f","tid":136138,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T00:12:46.000Z","msg":"就算香港有，都有班傻仔死坐到七點以表忠誠"},{"pid":"3e52d2916a0312406fc0ffda125fe18b3911af1c","tid":136138,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T00:14:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算香港有，都有班傻仔死坐到七點以表忠誠</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d6d172f172ab9e424567094a7088e21db6f357","tid":136138,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T00:16:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就算香港有，都有班傻仔死坐到七點以表忠誠</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n「嘩，咁早走呀....」"},{"pid":"bb7af051fd5bd6d37